Collaborative Reform Initiative for Technical Assistance (CRITA) program provides funding to advance the practice of community policing in law enforcement agencies by\nproviding technical assistance to state, local, territorial, and tribal law enforcement agencies on a variety of topics\nthat are tailored to meet their unique needs. This program provides practical “by the field, for the field” technical\nassistance from leading experts across a range of public safety, crime reduction, and community policing topics."
